					</w:rPr>
					<w:t>Question: If we eat spicy things, we begin to sweat. Why does this happen?</w:t>
				</w:r>
			</w:p>
			<w:p>
				<w:pPr>
					<w:spacing w:line="240" w:line-rule="auto" />
